They will charge you for things you do not get, then fail to deliver them or issue a credit- essentially STEALING FROM THEIR CUSTOMERS! Einstein's (aka Noah Bagels) is a chain bagel place that you can find in most major markets east of the Mississippi.  The bagels are all right for non kettle boiled and the sandwich variety is decent.  I wouldn't go out of my way to eat at Einstein's but if it's there and it's breakfast or lunch time Einstein's is a decent choice for a bagel with a schmear, an egg sandwich, and a surprisingly good cup of coffee.
Quick, friendly service. The bagels & bagel sandwiches are awesome here.
